  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/70f7d0847e4f9c389e95036886482ea1.avif?t=1619293899\" width=618 height=124 /></span><br><br>SJ-19 Learns to Love is a short boss focused metroidvania about a KILLER ROBOT who learns to love.  Fight and explore a mysterious planet while gaining ~EMOTIONAL MATURITY~ <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100+ rooms to EXTERMINATE. Including areas like BONE CITY and THE LAB. 🌎<br></li><li>8 bosses to battle, including BIG FROG and Steve the Milkman! 💀<br></li><li>Chat about ANIME with Tokotsu-kun 📺<br></li><li>Items to gain abilities and power, like MILK for some strong robot bones. 🥛<br></li><li>Frogs! Lots of them. 🐸<br></li><li>Collect SP to upgrade your gun, missiles, and others! 🔫<br></li><li>Learn to love! 💕</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/b9717b8823bf60e75328094e180c79ba.avif?t=1619293899\" width=618 height=139 /></span><br><br>Will SJ-19 fulfill their destiny as a KILLER ROBOT or learn to love and save everyone?!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/a678a42e3b9938fff99287fcad42f160.poster.avif?t=1619293899\" width=598 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/a678a42e3b9938fff99287fcad42f160.webm?t=1619293899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/a678a42e3b9938fff99287fcad42f160.mp4?t=1619293899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🥛💀 Are you BAD enough to defeat STEVE the milkman?! 💀🥛",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/70f7d0847e4f9c389e95036886482ea1.avif?t=1619293899\" width=618 height=124 /></span><br><br>SJ-19 Learns to Love is a short boss focused metroidvania about a KILLER ROBOT who learns to love.  Fight and explore a mysterious planet while gaining ~EMOTIONAL MATURITY~ <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100+ rooms to EXTERMINATE. Including areas like BONE CITY and THE LAB. 🌎<br></li><li>8 bosses to battle, including BIG FROG and Steve the Milkman! 💀<br></li><li>Chat about ANIME with Tokotsu-kun 📺<br></li><li>Items to gain abilities and power, like MILK for some strong robot bones. 🥛<br></li><li>Frogs! Lots of them. 🐸<br></li><li>Collect SP to upgrade your gun, missiles, and others! 🔫<br></li><li>Learn to love! 💕</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/b9717b8823bf60e75328094e180c79ba.avif?t=1619293899\" width=618 height=139 /></span><br><br>Will SJ-19 fulfill their destiny as a KILLER ROBOT or learn to love and save everyone?!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/a678a42e3b9938fff99287fcad42f160.poster.avif?t=1619293899\" width=598 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/a678a42e3b9938fff99287fcad42f160.webm?t=1619293899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441670/extras/a678a42e3b9938fff99287fcad42f160.mp4?t=1619293899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🥛💀 Are you BAD enough to defeat STEVE the milkman?! 💀🥛",
